---
layout: page
slug: about-us
---

%section#testimonials.hidden-xs
  %h1.sr-only Testimonials
  .container
    .row
      .col-sm-9
        #testimonials-carousel.carousel.slide{ data: { ride: "carousel", interval: 12000 }}
          %ol.carousel-indicators
            - data.testimonials.each do |i, t|
              - i = i.to_i
              %li{ class: "#{'active' if i == 0}", data: { target: "#testimonials-carousel", "slide-to" => i }}

          .carousel-inner
            - data.testimonials.each do |i, t|
              - i = i.to_i
              %div{ class: "item #{'active' if i == 0}" }
                = partial "index/testimonial", locals: { testimonial: t }

      #testimonials-action.col-sm-3
        %p Looking to build a Web or mobile app?
        = link_to "Get in touch", "/contact/", class: "btn btn-inverse"

%section#services
  %h1.sr-only Our Services
  .container
    .row
      .col-sm-6
        :kramdown
          We work closely with businesses in Australia and the UK to improve customer experience, increase sales, and simplify and automate their work with great software.

        %ul.row
          %li.service-design.col-sm-3.col-xs-6
            = iconic("pencil", modify: "fluid")
            Design
          %li.service-web.col-sm-3.col-xs-6
            = iconic("monitor", modify: "fluid")
            Web Apps
          %li.service-mobile.col-sm-3.col-xs-6
            = iconic("tablet", modify: "fluid")
            Mobile Apps
          %li.service-training.col-sm-3.col-xs-6
            = iconic("medal", modify: "fluid")
            Training

        = link_to "Case studies and more about our services", "/work/", class: "btn btn-default"

      .service-image.col-sm-6.hidden-xs
        = image_tag "/images/devices.png", width:"618", height:"328"

%section#about
  %h1.sr-only About Us
  .container
    .row
      #team.col-sm-6
        %h2 The Team
        %ul.row
          - ["robert", "dominic", "sam"].each do |name|
            = partial "index/team_member", locals: { username: name, member: data.team.send(name) }

      #history.col-sm-6
        %h2 About Terracoding
        :kramdown
          Terracoding is based in Sheffield and Manchester, UK. Weâ€™ve been working with clients internationally since 2011, advising on development strategy, designing interfaces users enjoy and writing fast, dependable code.

          We value testing and like to work in an #{define("Agile")} way, iterating on an idea with the client to produce the best solution.

%section#partners
  .container
    %h1 Clients &amp; Partners
    %ul#partner-logos
      - data.partners.each do |name, url|
        %li
          = link_to url do
            = image_tag "/images/partners/#{slugify(name)}.png", alt: name
